{
  "stem": "17308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 133.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then perhaps that year was that it wouldn't last long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we'd be able to come back, because we had confidence in the neighboring country, which was mainly France, that they should be able to intervene, and things might improve then.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only bare necessities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By car.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a few-- we had my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the cars from the business, and we traveled with the cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in our car there was, yeah, four.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We traveled together with our uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were with this family also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We traveled in two cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went towards the north-- well, I would say northwards towards the France-- like Rouen, we went that way-- Bordeaux.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually, in France itself, there were already organization-- French was directing people which direction to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many cars on the road.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all going mainly to France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was no other country, because the other side would have been Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was only one direction you could go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "France, you could go further if you wanted, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you didn't need travel documents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you had your identity paper, your passport and-- but even then, you didn't need to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Identity papers were sufficient.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was no problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The border was open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just showing it-- a way, where to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The French authorities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when you came to France, they showed you-- they were directing which way to go in France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wouldn't show you to go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were showing you to go southwards, towards the south of France",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not exactly, but we were following the road-- the instructions of the of the gendarmerie, the police, the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
